name: Tor Exit Node List - Threat Intel Plugin
summary: The Tor Exit Node List Lookup Table of the Threat Intel Plugin
description:
This content pack is part of the [Graylog Threat Intel Plugin](http://github.com/graylog-labs/graylog-plugin-threatintel).

*Please do not delete it manually if you consider to use the Threat Intel Plugin's functions. It contains important resources required by the plugin.*

This is the lookup table for the TOR (The Onion Router) Exit Node List, listing Exit Nodes of the TOR Network . This lookup table is used internally by Graylog's Threat Intel Plugin. Do not delete it manually.

description.value: This is the data adapter for the TOR (The Onion Router) Exit Node List, listing Exit Nodes of the TOR Network . This adapter is used internally by Graylog's Threat Intel Plugin. Do not delete it manually.
Certain downloaded lists do not require caching because they are in memory already and use this no-op cache.
